Class LinkedList<E>

  • java.lang.Object
    • cafe.util.LinkedList<E>

  • public class LinkedList<E>
extends java.lang.Object
    Linked list implementation of the list using a header node. Access to the list is via LinkedListItr.

    Mark Allen Weiss
